---

<section class="min-h-[90vh] flex items-center bg-gradient-to-br from-cream via-warm to-cream pt-24 md:pt-0">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
    <!-- Text -->
    <div class="reveal">
      <p class="text-secondary font-medium text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Terapeuta Pathwork®</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-brown leading-tight mb-6">
        Alcance <span class="text-primary">bem-estar</span>, maturidade e equilíbrio emocional
      </h1>
      <p class="text-brown/70 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Desperte sua maturidade emocional e reconecte-se com a essência que parecia esquecida. 
        Transforme medos e inseguranças em autoconfiança, clareza e equilíbrio interior.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
        <a href="#contato" class="bg-primary text-cream px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-center font-semibold hover:bg-primary/90 transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl">
          Agende uma Consulta
        </a>
        <a href="#metodo" class="border-2 border-primary text-primary px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-center font-semibold hover:bg-primary hover:text-cream transition-all">
          Conheça o Pathwork
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Image placeholder -->
    <div class="reveal flex justify-center">
      <div class="w-80 h-96 md:w-96 md:h-[28rem] rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/10 to-accent/10 flex items-center justify-center border-2 border-sand/30">
        <p class="text-brown/40 text-center px-8 font-medium">Foto profissional<br/>da Nyres</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
